    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Champ Resto Indonesia Tbk operates as a restaurant chain company in Indonesia. It engages in the operation of GRILLMAN, a Korean and Japanese restaurant; Gokana Ramen & Teppan, a full-service Japanese restaurant; Raa Cha Suki & BBQ, a self-service concept; Monsieur Spoon, a French artisan brand; and Dewata, which serves Indonesian food. The company also operates CROCO, a bakery café; BMK, which serves traditional Indonesian menus; Chopstix, which serves Asian fusion cuisines; and Platinum Resto & Café, which serves comfort food. In addition, it engages in the wholesale trade of coffee, tea, cocoa, bakery products, and food and beverages. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia.",
